      <div class="callouts">
        <div class="warn">â€¢ MultiQuery fan-out â†’ NÃ— DB searches before answering</div>
        <div class="warn">â€¢ Per-doc compression & rerank â†’ up to 2Ã—k extra LLM calls</div>
